# --- OS Junk Files (Catches Mac and Windows hidden files) ---
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# --- Python Backend Ignores ---
# The ** tells Git to look inside ALL subfolders (like your backend folder)
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd

# Virtual Environments (If you build one in the future)
venv/
env/
.venv/

# --- Security ---
# NEVER upload API keys or passwords. 
# If you ever create a .env file to hold passwords, this line protects it.
**/.env

# --- Frontend Ignores ---
# You are using CDNs right now, but if you ever upgrade to Node.js/Vite,
# this will stop Git from uploading the massive node_modules folder.
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/